 I might as well play a bit since I am already here.
 I turn to browse the shelf beside the piano.
 Today, I'll try looking through that Clementi sonatina I tried last time;
 after all, he definitely would not approve of me playing big works with
 my technique!
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
As I pull out the book and flip to the right page, I suddenly want to see
