\begin_layout Standard
Suddenly, I felt my feet and ankles harden.
 I look down and see to my surprise and horror that my legs are turning
 into salt.
 I drop the picture and desperately try to stand up, but soon my legs are
 completely hardened.
 My midsection follows suit, and soon I cannot even bend my back.
 I decide it really is time to go.
 I cross my arms over my chest as they harden into salt, and as the conversion
